lwichitsintu vice president of marketing executive director of planet communications asia pcl he was appointed to the board since 997 he holds a masters degree in business economics from kasetsart university thailand rungroj jaturaworaporn mr rungroj jaturaworaporn is vice president of sale of broadcast  digital tv of planet communications asia pcl since  he holds a bachelor of electronic engineering king mongkut’s institute of technology ladkrabang prawich rungdecharak mr prawich rungdecharak is vice president of technical services of planet communications asia pcl he was appointed to the board since  he holds a master of business administration from mahanakorn university of technology thailand wathara arun pramot phongthong somkit wangchoetchuwong katiya greigarn dr katiya greigarn is an independent director of planet communications asia pcl since  he is also a chairman of the audit committee in the company he holds a bachelor of electrical engineering from chulalongkorn university a masters degree in electrical engineering and a phd in electrical engineering from university of missouri sompong ouitrakul mr sompong ouitrakul is an independent director of planet communications asia pcl since  he is also a member of the audit committee in the company he holds a master of business administration from rangsit university thailand sutharak soonthornpusit mrs sutharak soonthornpusit is an independent director of planet communications asia pcl since  she is also a member of the audit committee in the company she holds a master of science in marketing and economics from ball state university usa basic compensation name fiscal year total sanpat sopon  prapat rathlertkarn  trevor thompson  ratana suwan  satit rathlertkarn  aneak pongsabutra  somchai sakulwichitsintu  rungroj jaturaworaporn  prawich rungdecharak  wathara arun  pramot phongthong  somkit wangchoetchuwong  katiya greigarn  sompong ouitrakul  sutharak soonthornpusit  as of  options compensation name options value